name: Maliss P White Rabbit
text: You take no battle damage from battles involving "Maliss" Link Monsters that point to this card. You can only use each of the following effects of "Maliss P White Rabbit" once per turn. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Set 1 "Maliss" Trap from your Deck with a different name from the cards in your GY. If this card is banished: You can pay 300 LP; Special Summon this card, also you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Link Monsters.
